d 'JQTE': module providing Journal Navigation Tool for Journal of Quantitative & Technological Economics
d
d  jqte command provides navigation functionality for the Journal
d of Quantitative & Technological    Economics , supporting
d browsing and downloading of journal articles and their
d attachments.	  This command directly accesses the official
d website data of Journal of Quantitative &    Technological
d Economics, supporting browsing and attachment downloads for all
d journal content    from 2018 to present. 
d
d KW: Journal of Quantitative & Technological Economics
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20250618
d
d Author: Wang Qiang, Xi'an Jiaotong University
d Support: email  740130359@@qq.com
d
f jqte.ado
f jqte.sthlp
